content:
Boost your sales teams' results with new features across Sales Cloud. Sales reps get a boost to their productivity with standard and custom list view actions in the Account, Contact, and Lead Intelligence views. Conversation Signals give sales teams a bird's-eye view of their conversations with customers.

Einstein for Sales:

* Let Einstein draft sales emails from a sales rep's inbox
* Visualize contacts in a relationship map
* Add buyer profile data to contacts automatically
* Draft meeting request emails using generative AI

Sales Foundations:

* Create contacts automatically from email and calendar activity
* Apply personal labels to organize records
* Get more information on the Seller Home page
* Boost productivity with standard and custom list view actions in Account, Contact, and Lead Intelligence views

Einstein Conversation Insights:

* Get a bird's-eye view of sales teams' conversations with Conversation Signals
* Create custom insights powered by generative AI
* Process single-user meetings
* Expand edit access to record collections

Sales Engagement:

* Link cadences and use screen flows as cadence steps
* Save cadences in any folder and create/edit email templates in Cadence Builder 2.0

Revenue Intelligence:

* Nurture relationships with stakeholders and identify opportunities to expand markets with lead metrics
* Update revenue data hourly and explore Revenue Insights resources

Collaborative Forecasts:

* Review forecast rollups by team, then by forecast group or product family

Pipeline Inspection:

* Get insight into potentially risky contacts on a deal

Sales Programs and Partner Tracks with Enablement:

* Give sales reps immediate feedback on their sales pitches
* Create programs that align with complex revenue metrics
* Integrate governance of Enablement rollout with other Salesforce systems and processes

Partner Relationship Management:

* Help draft personalized emails to contacts and leads quickly with Einstein generative AI

Sales Performance Management:

* Improve processing performance when plotting high-volume data
* Plan for and centralize company segmentation, territories, and quota targets in Sales Planning
* Determine compensation for reps based on territory assignment dates
title: Boosting Sales Productivity with New Salesforce Features
